Company Overview of Ivory Investment Management, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ivory Investment Management, L.P. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It uses in-house research to make its investments. Ivory Investment Management, L.P. was founded in November 1998 and is based in Los Angeles, California with an additional office in New York City.


